          <h2 class="title"><div><h1 class="hero-title">Russell<span> McLendon</span></h1></div></h2>    
          <div class="author-wrapper">
<div class="clearfix media-block"><div class="blogger-info-container"><p>Science journalist blogs about humans and other wildlife.</p><div class="wrap-links"><a class="more-about" href="/users/rmclendon">More about Russell</a> <a class="about-rss" href="/rss/rmclendon"><i class="icn-rss"></i> RSS feed</a></div></div>
